Theme format interop
---------------------

This plugin reads the "ThemeDB" theme.json manifest format used by
community CSS themes published to deckthemes.com. The format is
reused for compatibility with existing themes — no source code from
SDH-CSSLoader (the Decky-Loader CSS loader) was copied or
transliterated. The manifest schema is a functional interop format,
not creative expression.

